Create Slave
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount teslabs
Host imap.gmail.com
User gerard@teslabs.com
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.mailpass.gpg"
UseIMAPS yes
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore teslabs-remote
Account teslabs

MaildirStore teslabs-local
Path ~/mail/teslabs/
Inbox ~/mail/teslabs/INBOX

Channel teslabs-inbox
Master :teslabs-remote:INBOX
Slave :teslabs-local:INBOX

Channel teslabs-archive
Master ":teslabs-remote:[Gmail]/All Mail"
Slave :teslabs-local:archive

Channel teslabs-drafts
Master ":teslabs-remote:[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :teslabs-local:drafts

Channel teslabs-sent
Master ":teslabs-remote:[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :teslabs-local:sent

Channel teslabs-trash
Master ":teslabs-remote:[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :teslabs-local:trash

Channel teslabs-spam
Master ":teslabs-remote:[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :teslabs-local:spam

Group teslabs
Channel teslabs-inbox
Channel teslabs-archive
Channel teslabs-drafts
Channel teslabs-sent
Channel teslabs-trash
Channel teslabs-spam
